Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.77,0:00:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.77,0:00:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.28,0:00:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.55,0:00:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.43,0:00:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.18,0:00:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.42,0:01:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.66,0:01:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.96,0:01:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.10,0:01:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.62,0:01:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫日暮篱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.09,0:01:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生于一个\N历史很悠久很古老的神社里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.00,0:01:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个非常平凡的国三女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.37,0:01:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就在我十五岁生日那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.07,0:01:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社的井里\N突然出现了一个妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.84,0:01:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我带回到了战国时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.44,0:01:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那里\N遇到了一个半妖少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.31,0:02:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他名叫犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.78,0:02:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有\N可以增强妖怪法力的宝玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.95,0:02:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.92,0:02:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了跟犬夜叉他们\N一起寻找散落各处的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.36,0:02:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始来往于\N现代与战国之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.10,0:02:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想借四魂之玉的力量\N满足自己的欲望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.98,0:02:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫奈落的妖怪为了从\N犬夜叉的哥哥杀生丸的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.95,0:02:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到完美的妖力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.08,0:02:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意将杀生丸引进奈落城里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.15,0:02:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正当奈落打算吞了杀生丸\N将他化成自己的一部分的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.06,0:02:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉偏偏破了奈落的结界\N跑进奈落城来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.46,0:02:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的  风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.13,0:02:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.76,0:02:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.47,0:02:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.77,0:02:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在千钧一发之际\N救兵及时赶到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.67,0:03:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.11,0:03:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.41,0:03:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真以为一辈子\N都能逃出我的手掌心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.91,0:03:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落利用珊瑚的弟弟\N琥珀做他的掩护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁机逃之夭夭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.09,0:03:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此\N真的从我们的面前消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.69,0:03:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第82话 奔波于现代与战国之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可恶了  奈落这个坏蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.20,0:03:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道以后\N他都不再回这座城了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连结界都被你破除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.64,0:03:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又怎么能搬走这座城堡呢\N你说对吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.82,0:03:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.52,0:03:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再给我一次机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.15,0:03:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定\N真的可以砍死奈落这个坏蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.29,0:03:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏就差那么一点点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.36,0:03:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.57,0:04:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢天谢地\N总算又可以回到学校了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算回到了这个安全的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.38,0:04:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻松松的念书了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.95,0:04:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想\N还真有点对不起犬夜叉他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得大家现在好不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.46,0:04:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个公式  后天一定会考哦\N大家回去要牢牢的把它背住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模拟考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.04,0:04:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都什么时候了\N还在担心别人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.97,0:04:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩两天\N要是不赶快抱抱佛脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.54,0:04:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候恐怕要补考那就惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  可以走了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.71,0:04:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.85,0:04:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.98,0:04:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你啦  借我笔记本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你这么可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.55,0:04:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们自己也要复习呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.36,0:04:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托拜托一下下就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.99,0:05:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只借一下下\N就还给你们总可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.93,0:05:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  谁叫你这么弱不禁风\N一天到晚生病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.36,0:05:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又是你最好的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.93,0:05:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.13,0:05:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你们一定会帮我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就拿去影印一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就还给你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.64,0:05:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.14,0:05:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得这么可怜\N我们哪敢不借呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就谢谢咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.01,0:05:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.25,0:05:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家开动吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.76,0:05:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在胡思乱想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.77,0:05:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想什么还用说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.60,0:05:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是那个\N爱吃醋的小太保是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想别的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别装了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他到底怎么样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事到底怎么样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你发展到什么程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.12,0:05:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天才见过他哥哥而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说见过他哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他哥哥恐怕也是太保吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.69,0:06:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他哥哥这么凶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.29,0:06:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他哥哥应该更厉害一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.13,0:06:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们兄弟俩只要一碰面\N经常都会打架呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.63,0:06:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两兄弟都不是好惹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.64,0:06:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你打算继续这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.87,0:06:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心你将来吃亏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒认为\N爱可以克服一切障碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇我支持你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.39,0:06:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我借走笔记了  谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.59,0:06:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学生正在考试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.66,0:06:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的目的都跟戈薇一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办?要去排队吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.90,0:06:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是影印去哪里都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到其他地方去印吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.67,0:06:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么到处都这么多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.34,0:06:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞么鬼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.84,0:06:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下怎么办啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.81,0:07:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们该回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.55,0:07:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝…祝你好运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.35,0:07:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.86,0:07:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.26,0:07:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是些没有义气的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇这家伙\N不晓得为什么去那么久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.14,0:07:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说好了\N马上就会回来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对\N她说过要待两三天才回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.77,0:07:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  稍安勿躁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.88,0:07:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么每一个人\N都好像没事一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.65,0:07:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落从我们手中跑掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是第一次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.15,0:07:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更别说是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.79,0:07:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为你也应该养足精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.95,0:07:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才有力气继续对付奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  你在胡说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.89,0:07:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不像你们几个家伙\N这么不堪一击呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不觉得疲倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.16,0:07:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那种打法\N普通人还真是受不了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己身子差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好意思怪别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.25,0:08:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.95,0:08:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.95,0:08:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落的邪气还阴魂不散呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.52,0:08:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来都让那些死魂虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙寻找他那股邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.49,0:08:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次偏偏\N连结界的位置都感应不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.13,0:08:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底奈落那股邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.77,0:08:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏到什么地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.91,0:08:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.14,0:08:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上从琥珀身上\N取下四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.88,0:08:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你只当\N这个小子是个傀儡的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.92,0:08:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就不会\N帮你解决那个人质姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.02,0:08:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会送上门让杀生丸杀他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.40,0:08:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再这么继续反抗奈落下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看\N你恐怕没多少日子可活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.94,0:09:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我光会说别人  而我自己呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落失踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.19,0:09:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连琥珀也一起不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.57,0:09:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.98,0:09:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来弥勒法师\N特地去安慰珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.18,0:09:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是这样没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.09,0:09:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇早就跟我说过\N珊瑚一定在偷偷期待琥珀回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母  我可以坐一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.46,0:10:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子你还在担心\N你弟弟的事对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.23,0:10:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么说有点强人所难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.87,0:10:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你真的要放宽心才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.11,0:10:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我能够了解你的感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.75,0:10:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候\N你是不是想一个人静一静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.39,0:10:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要说的就这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.39,0:10:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  弥勒法师最恶心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假装要安慰人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.27,0:10:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是想趁机吃豆腐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.87,0:10:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.27,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一天等很久了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛不早点跟我说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.51,0:10:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的声音特别清脆好听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个都只会偷懒\N一点都不知道上进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.65,0:11:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子\N还是得自己挑灯夜战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一点都看不懂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.07,0:11:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想想办法才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  请问哲子在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电话里问问也行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.07,0:11:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.08,0:11:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.44,0:11:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.18,0:11:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚在电话里面问了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.19,0:11:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐  你的课本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.19,0:11:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果昨天一整天\N什么都没有做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  姐姐  告诉你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.46,0:11:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打断我听到没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易背住了\N又让你给打断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天再背不起来的话\N真的会完蛋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉他来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.34,0:11:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.61,0:11:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是专程来接你的  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.34,0:11:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  马上跟我回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要捣乱好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要考试了你知不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.22,0:12:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又发什么小姐脾气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.48,0:12:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.12,0:12:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我乖乖的  知不知道\N绝对不可以到外头去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖待在家里你听到了没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.63,0:12:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.63,0:12:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.13,0:12:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  我傍晚就回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.37,0:12:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.74,0:12:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇已经走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.14,0:12:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.87,0:12:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇忘了把便当带走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.51,0:12:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.88,0:12:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.01,0:12:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得能不能麻烦你跑一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沿着戈薇身上的气味找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很快可以追上她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮忙  马上给我抓住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚  全都给我闪开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.28,0:13:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子\N你活得不耐烦了是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.89,0:13:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来戈薇她们这个时代\N也安全不到哪里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.70,0:13:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在发什么呆啊  快过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.71,0:14:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看什么看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.26,0:14:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵好可爱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.46,0:14:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你搞什么鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.36,0:14:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.50,0:14:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥  谢谢你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要命\N这世界怎么乱成这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么事啊  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.66,0:15:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.67,0:15:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.53,0:15:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉怎么会在这里出现呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.31,0:15:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.05,0:15:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚是你叫坐下的吧\N麻烦你站起来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.56,0:15:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么鬼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.57,0:15:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出门前不是跟你说过\N叫你千万不要出门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.07,0:15:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很烦耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有什么办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有人托我来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人托你来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.58,0:15:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.32,0:15:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的便当耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.45,0:15:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道专程替我送便当来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.05,0:16:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们分着吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.73,0:16:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都挤成一堆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.84,0:16:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家里温书\N根本就没有办法专心嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子\N只好在图书馆待到天黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.34,0:16:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快点念就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.38,0:16:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的肋间神经痛好多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.62,0:16:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪轻轻居然身体那么差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.35,0:16:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要好好锻炼才行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.62,0:16:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一些对健康有益的食谱\N是我特别搜集来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.13,0:16:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿回去试一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.40,0:16:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.87,0:16:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条这个人真的好细心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.74,0:16:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.14,0:16:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚怎么没有想到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.14,0:16:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然忘了跟北条借笔记来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.92,0:17:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我  北条同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.50,0:17:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.96,0:17:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.90,0:17:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  突然想起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.67,0:17:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有个中药偏方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说对各种病都很有帮助呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.97,0:17:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.24,0:17:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  戈薇同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.84,0:17:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体健康呢最重要的是情绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要让自己的生活有规律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.01,0:17:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三餐也要定时定量哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.69,0:17:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇同学  记得一定要吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.26,0:17:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等  北条同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.20,0:17:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  北条同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.50,0:17:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真倒霉  还是没有借到笔记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.51,0:17:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐  你看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.31,0:18:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.11,0:18:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.55,0:18:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像刚刚说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.55,0:18:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一位\N身穿红衣身轻如燕的年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.18,0:18:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最后紧要关头\N帮忙抓到了强盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.65,0:18:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.05,0:18:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位年轻人的\N英勇事迹不只这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.29,0:18:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还帮消防队\N救出被困在大火中的小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.29,0:18:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉哥哥好厉害哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.63,0:18:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那位年轻人的画像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.53,0:18:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是刚刚我戴的帽子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.77,0:18:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去学校之前你到底做过什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.17,0:18:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别说这些  这盒子装什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.66,0:18:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.33,0:18:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书都念不完了  还在吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.17,0:19:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太  你进来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.67,0:19:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐  什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我陪犬夜叉哥哥玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.87,0:19:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉哥哥  我们去泡澡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.81,0:19:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.88,0:19:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续看书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.58,0:19:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫  搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.32,0:19:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能出去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.19,0:19:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥皂都还没有冲掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.39,0:19:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少罗唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.06,0:19:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不玩了\N出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.36,0:19:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你出去你听到了没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.10,0:19:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公式又忘得一干二净了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.74,0:19:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们一起吃饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.81,0:19:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算安静下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.85,0:19:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舌头快烧掉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.62,0:19:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了咖哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.88,0:19:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是辣到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.09,0:19:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辣死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.09,0:19:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你自己像饿死鬼一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到东西就往嘴里塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.61,0:20:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.81,0:20:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么叫\N你很烦知不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.58,0:20:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样一直看着我\N我会分心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.38,0:20:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你还是躺下来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.55,0:20:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.92,0:20:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你眼睛不看着前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.25,0:20:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东张西望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.79,0:20:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了\N明天可以跟我回去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.46,0:20:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.76,0:20:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子\N难道打算整晚都盯着我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.80,0:20:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.27,0:20:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么精力充沛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.48,0:20:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡  睡着啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不晓得这小子搞什么鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.85,0:21:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家要温书偏偏来搅局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.43,0:21:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是犬夜叉这副熟睡的模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.87,0:21:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前还真的没有见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也难怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.38,0:21:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最忙最累的一向就是他嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.52,0:21:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少今天晚上\N你可以好好的睡一觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.37,0:21:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.74,0:21:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你昨天晚上\N在戈薇家过夜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.51,0:21:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.77,0:21:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无精打采的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.91,0:21:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是都怪你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.14,0:21:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你昨天晚上\N整晚都霸占我的床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.11,0:22:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后我连模拟考都考砸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.48,0:22:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最可恶的人就是你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.79,0:22:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气真不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.53,0:22:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟要流多少泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.37,0:22:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every Heart  才能坦白面对自己呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.48,0:22:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若对谁传达情感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.78,0:22:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every Heart  是否就能得到满足呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.09,0:22:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕着漫长漫长的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.90,0:22:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着遥远的星星祈祷着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.27,0:23:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.81,0:23:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都在寻找真正的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.62,0:23:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望自己能够变得更坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.26,0:23:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要抬头看着高高的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.26,0:23:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.87,0:23:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都在寻找生命的意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.62,0:23:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始发问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.85,0:23:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉碎片  根本不在奈落手里\N你说会是谁拿走了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.33,0:23:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我数数\N在琥珀背上有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.56,0:23:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇手里还有三个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.53,0:23:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.30,0:23:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停  时间到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.56,0:23:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖狼族的钢牙\N两只脚上也有两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.97,0:24:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一钢牙也被奈落抓到的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.04,0:24:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点你放心  奈落现在不知道\N躲到什么地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.61,0:24:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?这又是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.34,0:24:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回的犬夜叉是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.81,0:24:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖狼族少女和月虹的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.78,0:24:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说妖狼族少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.31,0:24:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别忘了还有钢牙呢



